nted effects such asdrop shadows and support for fonts up to 127 points.andM;The program ships with updated population data files.andP;  Additional demographicand marketing data and a variety of map boundary sets are available fromSelect Micro.andM;Version 4.0 is available immediately.andP;  Upgrades are $75 but free to userswith proof of purchase since June 30.andM;Select Micro Systems Inc. is located at 322 Underhill Ave., Yorktown Heights,N.Y.andP;  10598; (914) 245-4670.andP;  n</TEXT></DOC>